{"tid":498388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「啡膠樽」原來只係做樣，其實倒去堆填區！","createTime":"2017-12-13T17:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T07:23:33.000Z","uid":29314,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7a64fc6eed357d9f929eed7799b2e8d9bdf5485b","tid":498388,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:39:30.000Z","msg":"1號樽(即PET、聚脂纖維塑膠樽)的回收率也每況愈下，由2014年的14%下挫至15年的7.6%。 綠惜地球向政府部門索取了2015、16年的廢膠回收數據，其中2015年共回收到4863公噸廢膠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">綠惜地球推算，在7.6%回收數據中，政府支撐起其中的6個至7.3個百分點，意味自由市場只回收0.3至1.6%的回收</span> ，即平均每日僅回收1.6萬個至9.4萬個膠樽，這與全港每日棄置500多萬個膠樽相比，實屬九牛一毛。"},{"pid":"2d6061a08c44600ccf2003a3db550cff59af626a","tid":498388,"uid":8500,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:41:38.000Z","msg":"所以平時都係掉橙色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2a3e142615ad03a36ac8f040c1a025af69705a","tid":498388,"uid":26389,"like":37,"dislike":9,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"唉燒Q曬佢咪算囉 新加玻的焚化爐燒完得番0.1%體積 無大污染"},{"pid":"bcc779013bd63946026db0472a0ba8b1bde47e5f","tid":498388,"uid":140604,"like":1,"dislike":86,"score":-85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉燒Q曬佢咪算囉 新加玻的焚化爐燒完得番0.1%體積 無大污染</blockquote><br />\n燒埋你春袋呀燒"},{"pid":"0e98a1148b1408a901e403b2d71df0ab34ffc385","tid":498388,"uid":146924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:20:17.000Z","msg":"公開嘅秘密嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210b902b1d8996aad99108bad8fdb9265f5cb1b1","tid":498388,"uid":29270,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉燒Q曬佢咪算囉 新加玻的焚化爐燒完得番0.1%體積 無大污染</blockquote><br />\n燒埋你春袋呀燒</blockquote><br />\n高質素留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cee9fac1988eaa63d44179089652eb8d71faaf2",